messages.messageBody:
Hi Kathryn,

I started a group for unschoolers wanting to travel together. There
is a trip being planned to India in '09, and some list members are
thinking of planning an unschooling cruise, among other ideas
floating around. Check it out - maybe you'll find people interested
in a dive trip.

http://groups.yahoo.com/group/TRAVULL/

Happy traveling!
Neha
